query:
INSERT INTO request_history (
                id,
                endpoint_id,
                name,
                is_custom_name,
                active,
                method,
                headers,
                body,
                query
            )
            VALUES (
                ?,  -- id
                ?,  -- endpoint_id
                ?,  -- name
                ?,  -- is_custom_name
                ?,  -- active
                ?,  -- method
                ?,  -- headers
                ?,  -- body
                ?   -- query
            )
